        | essential for establishing credibility and attracting customers. However, many startups
        | struggle with the time and resources required to build a high-quality website from
        | scratch.

      .ms-paragraph
        | That's where Moonshot CSS Framework comes in. Our monochrome-based, brand-customizable
        | framework enables rapid deployment of startup corporate websites without sacrificing
        | quality or flexibility.

      h2.ms-heading-3.ms-mt-8.ms-mb-4 Why Monochrome?

      .ms-paragraph A monochrome foundation provides several key advantages:

      ul.ms-list.ms-list-unordered
        li.ms-list-item Timeless, professional aesthetic that works for any industry
        li.ms-list-item Client brand colors stand out without competing with framework colors
        li.ms-list-item Easier to maintain consistent contrast ratios for accessibility
        li.ms-list-item Reduces decision fatigue during the design process

      .ms-blockquote
        | "Moonshot CSS enabled us to launch our corporate site in just 10 days, with a design
        | that perfectly matches our brand identity."

      h2.ms-heading-3.ms-mt-8.ms-mb-4 Key Features for Startups

      .ms-paragraph
        | We've designed Moonshot specifically with startup needs in mind, including seven
        | essential page templates: front page, service pages, blog, events, recruitment, about
        | us, and brand family showcase.

      .ms-paragraph
        | Each template is optimized for SEO, mobile-responsive, and accessible out of the box.
        | This means you can focus on your content and business goals rather than technical
        | implementation details.

